<pre>The Cultural Club has the important responsibility of keeping their fellow Students entertained. This Club tries to break the monotony that creeps into lives of students and refresh them. It gives all the musicians, dancers and actors a chance to display their talents. The idea is to achieve dual goals of entertainment and professional development at a single go. The Cultural club is always ready with new and unique ideas taking the Juit talent to new heights. The sheer creativity of the club makes it different from all the other clubs of Juit.</pre>